protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of existing buildings and temporary partial loss of existing open space (Athlone Gardens) to facilitate redevelopment to provide new residential accommodation of up to 1000 units, up to a maximum of 3,104 square metres (GEA) of non residential floorspace (within Classes A1, A2, A3, A5 and/or Class B1 Use Classes), reprovision of community facilities and associated outdoor adventure playspace (total 1,883 square metres) (within Use Classes D1 and D2), relocation and reprovision of an area of open space (Athlone Gardens) (9,186 square metres), reprovision of 20 lock ups (within Use Class B8), provision of up to 604 car parking spaces (on street and off street) and 1177 cycle parking spaces.
